##

@node Requirement "System and Hardware requirements"
@prev Introduction
@next Copyright

@{b}Software and hardware requirements.@{ub}

You need OS 2.0 or better, MUI system installed (©Stefan Stuntz),  ZIP
100  drive (SCSI version) from IOMEGA and any amiga equipped with SCSI
controller.

@endnode

